    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的音乐解谜机制</h2>玩家走进《Sonority》之后，将面临一个失落的世界，音乐在这里仿佛魔法一般，你要利用音符和旋律才能不断推进游戏进程。<br><br>破解这些谜题需要正确排列音符，解法需要通过声音方面的推断或者利用符号，不需要事先具备乐理知识。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432390/extras/205061b657a52b5bb03de74b7d06985d.poster.avif?t=1746012048\" width=614 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432390/extras/205061b657a52b5bb03de74b7d06985d.webm?t=1746012048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432390/extras/205061b657a52b5bb03de74b7d06985d.mp4?t=1746012048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>玩家化身年轻的艾斯特，为了帮助朋友踏上冒险旅途。带着排箫，来到神秘的石园，可是很快就会遇到障碍，必须借助音乐的力量克服难关，有些可不太好克服。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432390/extras/473d44316628e322294c6bed27b51c71.avif?t=1746012048\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br>艾斯特走进一片寂静的世界，依靠会唱歌的石头和会说话的浣熊，再次发现了失落的乐曲和爬满苔藓的画作，可是传说中的音乐老师却无处可寻。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432390/extras/487431554391f084839b32f95c9dfaf8.poster.avif?t=1746012048\" width=614 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432390/extras/487431554391f084839b32f95c9dfaf8.webm?t=1746012048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432390/extras/487431554391f084839b32f95c9dfaf8.mp4?t=1746012048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432390/extras/e84430878b6f94e62f87ba48c2ddc15c.avif?t=1746012048\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br>游戏越到后面，谜题就越棘手。即便是传奇大师最难的谜题，多多收集音符和乐器，也就有可能破解。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432390/extras/e5e1922d6861a63ca510d921ad7d03c9.poster.avif?t=1746012048\" width=614 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432390/extras/e5e1922d6861a63ca510d921ad7d03c9.webm?t=1746012048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432390/extras/e5e1922d6861a63ca510d921ad7d03c9.mp4?t=1746012048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>有趣、新奇的音乐解谜机制，简单的音符序列逐渐变成短小的旋律，然后变成复杂的乐章。<br></li><li>一段动人的故事，在艾斯特和一只怪脾气老浣熊跟他会唱歌的石头朋友之间展开。<br></li><li>3D游戏世界，设计精妙，连贯流畅，场景多样。<br></li><li>原创音乐丰富多彩、氛围浓厚，包含英文、德文两个版本。<br></li><li>支持键盘和控制器。</li></ul>",
